Multi Auto Product Model

The Multi Auto product is a multi-instance product model that lets users create quotes for multiple vehicles driven by multiple drivers. 
Insured Item: Vehicle
The Insured Item Spec is the spec for vehicles to be insured.
Insured Party: Driver
The insured party spec represents drivers for an auto insurance product. 
Coverages for Auto Products
Coverage specs define the required and optional coverages on an insurance product.
Multi Auto Root Product
The root product spec is the container for the Multi Auto product model.
Attributes for Auto Products
All the attributes used in the Auto insurance product are defined in the Vlocity Attribute Designer.
Rules for Auto Products
The Multi Auto product includes a number of rules.
Surcharges for Auto Products
The Multi Auto insurance root product includes several surcharges set up to be calculated when quotes are created and policies are modified.
Simulate Rating the Multi Auto Product
The Simulate tab on the root product spec has the ratings set up to simulate rating the Multi Auto product model.
title: Understanding Multi Auto Insurance Products
